Title: Ward-Takahashi Identities in Large N Field Theories

Authors: M. Araki and Y. Tanii

Comments: 8 pages, LaTeX

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B383 (1996) 322-326

The Ward-Takahashi identities in large N field theories are expressed in asimple form using master fields. Operators appearing in these expressions arefound to be generators of symmetry transformations acting on the master fields.